{"tid":2371784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢封城前影片曝光 證阻採訪","createTime":"2021-01-19T06:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T07:02:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3ee6fb2e687a36a436df323fc9c6178dc7596d","tid":2371784,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210119/KTH6TMVCWFGUFLIFKR3JHASIQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210119%2FKTH6TMVCWFGUFLIFKR3JHASIQE%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=b4fe8552\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210119%2FKTH6TMVCWFGUFLIFKR3JHASIQE%2F&h=bc44d33c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210119/KTH6TMVCWFGUFLIFKR3JHASIQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢封城前影片曝光 證阻採訪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e6lBVfcFmaET61iO-J4VW19Nybg=/1640x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GXQYD76Y5BDX5FQ7UQDAJ3XTWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe6lBVfcFmaET61iO-J4VW19Nybg%3D%2F1640x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGXQYD76Y5BDX5FQ7UQDAJ3XTWI.jpg&h=48b30a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半島電視台昨日播出武漢封城前三日，由兩名中國記者秘密錄下的影片，揭露中國政府未致力防止疫情散播、卻阻撓記者報道疫情爆發。<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，卡塔爾半島電視台播出特別節目「絆住全世界的3天」，播放未曾公開的畫面，是由兩名中國記者在2020年1月19至22日拍攝，而武漢在1月23日開始封城。報道指，這些畫面無法在中國播映，半島電視台調查部門將影片偷運出中國。為了兩名記者安全，以化名楊駿、陳偉稱呼兩人。他們在去年1月19日抵達武漢時，仍未知疫情嚴重程度，而病毒是否會人傳人亦未證實，武漢人對於爆發疫情的問題相對無動於衷。<br />\n<br />\n兩名記者穿梭於日益爆滿的不同醫院之間，並前往被指為武肺疫情可能源頭的華南海鮮批發市場，卻一再遭到公安阻擋（圖）。當局稱正調查病毒起源，市場已被關閉，但武漢與北京的官員都不打算揭露疫情的嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n竭力瞞疫致病毒擴散<br />\n<br />\n在數以百萬計民眾正為之後的農曆新年而旅行、聚集之際，中國政府突然宣佈封城，令原本態度馬虎的民眾，在數小時內變得驚慌失措，幾乎所有人都戴上口罩，但為時已晚。<br />\n<br />\n半島電視台在報道中指出：「外界普遍認為，中國政府在最開始那幾天不說明和不透明，是病毒得以如此迅速散播的原因之一，造就了超過200萬人病故的這場百年大疫。」<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"f1f5d47ba821250b0b0a210f1733b82b6f7e31ae","tid":2371784,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"半島電視台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417a76354b46e0e064004fbae27e3c056f5e7a8","tid":2371784,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"中共：假新聞"},{"pid":"427a0bee6e0cafffc18264e53e41b7dd7d8826b1","tid":2371784,"uid":301952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"點止三日呀<br />\n連登第一個武肺post 都唔止三日前啦"},{"pid":"2a9f5338a39e5086b83f51910a06d9e1f4e618eb","tid":2371784,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ec82a01511dda2b7f71a34bad11beb3192541e","tid":2371784,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4417a76354b46e0e064004fbae27e3c056f5e7a8","tid":2371784,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"中共：假新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"拜登: 假新聞 抹黑中國"},{"pid":"65c6f26b759cff89efdcc6c768680252b9a28533","tid":2371784,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"拜燈：你班記者好嘔心"},{"pid":"20eaefc6c97b0d10716e6db91ba3b3df52b18c91","tid":2371784,"uid":347528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"係中國為咗保護記者健康，用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f579ced18d818b3536cf86b8b91035a718867411","tid":2371784,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d98f62cd35086b36a0643ef22be0a7abfd1039","tid":2371784,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"中國人會話，領導未公佈，散佈影片是在造謠<br />\n<br />\n佢地點都諗到一個罪名俾人去合理化自己"}]}